Improve Data Quality by Monitoring Problem Record Metrics: Records that aren’t ingested into Data Cloud due to data quality issues are logged in a problem records data lake object (DLO)

You can query and map the problem records DLO to identify and address data quality issues. When: August 2024. How: Access via Refresh History tab, properties, Query Editor, Data Explorer, Query API.
